item.dc:creator: @Eh_Pretty_Easy Eh Pretty Easy
item.description:
@Eh_Pretty_Easy wrote:

[quote=“Mr.Chris, post:8, topic:89172”][quote author=Criptic link=topic=130405.msg1263120#msg1263120 date=1178315863]
i think it is a big hoax lol well cmon its like slavery its even worse than minimum wage but hang on wait 4 x 30 = 120 holy shite im going to china to get a job 120$ a month for playing games wooohoo
[/quote]

Your a complete retard. Exploitation happens everyday. The clothes your wearing now are probably made by little kids getting $0.30 a day in Ethiopia.

These gold farmers exploit Chinese and Korean men who are trying to make money to keep their children alive. They are getting such a little amount a day, that they are hardly able to feed their kids, let alone give them a home.

You’d probably get $10 a month for clicking for 17 hours a day.

So, I repeat, Criptic. You’re a complete, and utter, idiot.[/quote]How is it that some of the Chinese people can afford members…? Or are they just bots.
